programme.desc: For en nyexaminerad polis finns det en sak som ar farligare an att visa upp en mordares fantasi. Att bli den.

programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Man On A Ledge (2012)
programme.desc: Vågar du ta nasta steg? Den forrymde fången Nick Cassidy står plotsligt hogt upp på en avsats på en skyskrapa i New York. Kommer han att hoppa? På nolltid har Nick fångat hela stadens och alla mediers uppmarksamhet. Och medan alla tittar upp, ser ingen den utstuderade kupp som ager rum på andra sidan gatan. Hanger dessa båda handelser ihop? Kommer polispsykologen Lydia sanningen på spåren? Och har Nick i sjalva verket en helt annan agenda?

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: En astronomiprofessor som jobbat for NASA inser att en destruktiv asteroid ar på kollisionskurs med jorden och måste få sin familj i sakerhet samtidigt som han varnar varlden for denna hotande forodelse.

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in China
programme.desc: Det ar sent 1800-tal i sydostra Kina, och kungfumastaren Wong Fei Hung ar det enda som står mellan hans hemregion och ockupationsmakten som redan tagit kontrollen over Hongkong och Macao. Samtidigt som den legendariska folkhjalten Wong slåss for sitt och folkets liv, spirar en romans med den oemotståndliga Siu-kwan. Once Upon a Time in China ar Jet Lis forsta film i rollen som Wong Fei Hung, och betraktas som en av hongkongfilmens gyllene eras framsta filmer.

programme.title: Saints and Soldiers
programme.desc: I mitten av december 1944 rycker Hitlers arme fram genom Ardennesskogen in i Belgien. Furir Nathan Greer och hans nara van Gordon Gunderson blir liksom hundratals andra amerikanska soldater tillfångatagna av nazisterna mitt ute på ett kallt och snotackt falt. Allt eftersom utbryter panik och forvirring nar de tyska soldaterna borjar skjuta de amerikanska fångarna. Greer, Gunderson och en handfull andra soldater lyckas fly undan tyskarna. Utan varken vapen eller mat går de en hård och kall vinter till motes i hopp om att hitta tillbaka till det område dar de allierade befinner sig. En lång och mycket farlig vandring borjar.

programme.title: Godsend
programme.desc: Efter deras unga sons dod kommer Paul och Jessie Duncan overens om att få honom klonad av en mystisk lakare. Saker och ting tar en olycksbådande vandning nar deras nya son vaxer upp och de lar sig en chockerande hemlighet om lakaren.

programme.title: Walking Tall
programme.desc: Nar det galler att skipa lag och ratt kan en man gora skillnad! Actionstjarnan Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson tar inga fångar nar han kampar for rattvisa och krossar korruption i denna berattelse om en man som tar stallning… och tar tillbaka sin stad!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Delta Farce
programme.desc: En trio klumpiga vanner misstas for soldater och satts på ett plan till Irak. Men efter att ha kastats ut på vagen befinner de sig overgivna i en by ar i desperat behov av hjalp. Kan de bli hjaltar på riktigt?

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Sightings
programme.desc: Ett science fiction-mysterium om en dysfunktionell familj som bor på en ranch i Texas och hotas av en varelse i skogen. For att kunna overleva hotet måste de samtidigt losa sina egna inre konflikter.

programme.title: Supersnooper
programme.desc: Terence Hill ar den nyutbildade polismannen Dave Speed, som ska inkassera en parkeringsbot mitt i ett olandigt traskområde. Tyvarr ar det också platsen for ett topphemligt atombombsprov. Dave får en rejal dos radioaktivitet, vilket ger honom overnaturliga krafter! Han klarar fall från hoga skyskrapor och flyttar saker med tankekraft. Daves kollega Willy (Ernest Borgnine) vagrar in i det langsta att inse att Dave verkligen har superkrafter - något som alla skurkar dock får kanna på.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Dom kallar mej Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand
programme.desc: Denna vildsinta parodi på ""7 vågade livet"" gjorde Spencer/Hill till stjarnor! Han har en kaft lika valoljad som hans revolver. Han har ett rykte lika smutsigt som kladerna han rider i. Han sager att han ar en fredens man - men vem vågar tro honom? Hans namn ar Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand. I stan traffar Trinity sin ohangde bror Bambino och de kommer i bråk med den skurkaktige Majoren som forsoker ta over stan. Men Trinity och Bambino moter hotet med det enda språk som bovar forstår kulor och storsmockor!

programme.title: Trinity klipper till igen
programme.desc: Men hor och hapna: Nu har de slagit sig på en karriar som hemliga poliser, med uppdrag att satta fast ett storsmugglande banditgang. For bra for att vara sant? Ja faktiskt, for de ar sjalva ute efter att håva in formogenheten. Och for att vinna guld kommer de offra mycket bly.Men till skillnad från andra vilda fighter och skottdueller finns har många vinnare. Vapentillverkare, bandageforsaljare och dodgravare till exempel. Och framforallt lakarna som måste ta hand om alla som skrattat kakarna ur led! Terence Hill and Bud Spencer ar ett av filmhistoriens popularaste hjaltepar, som dunkat skurkar ihop I nitton filmer!

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Hardcore
programme.desc: Du minns ingenting av ditt tidigare liv. Allt du vet ar att du heter Henry, något din fru berattade nar hon nyss återupplivade dig från de doda. Bara några minuter senare blir du beskjuten och din fru kidnappas. Den skyldige till dådet ar Akan, en maktig krigsherre omgiven av en arme av legosoldater, som planerar att ta over varlden. Plotsligt befinner du dig i Moskva dar alla vill se dig dod. Alla utom en mystisk engelsman, Jimmy. Men kan du verkligen lita på honom? Om du bara overlever vansinnet kommer du forstå meningen med allt och sanningen bakom din identitet. Lycka till Henry – du kommer sannolikt behova det…

programme.title: The Condemned 2
programme.desc: Nar han misslyckas med att fånga ledaren for en dodlig spelring blir prisjagaren Will Tanner den jagade — ett manskligt mål i ett spel dar de som ar med måste doda eller bli dodade.

programme.title: Skumma polare
programme.desc: Trinityseriens stjarna Bud Spencer återvander till vilda vastern i regissoren Michele Lupo’s komedi om bedragaren Buddy, som misstas for en lakare efter att hans van Cocoa oavsiktligt stjal en resvaska med kirurgiska instrument. Buddy bosatter sig i den lilla staden som en experimentell lakare. Nar ett gang våldsamma brottslingar forsoker ta over staden, visar det sig att hans sanna talang ar att slå ner skurkar synkad till musik som humoristiskt komponerats av spaghettivastmastaren Ennio Morricone.

programme.title: Occupation
programme.desc: Efter att deras stad har utplånats av ett massivt flyganfall lyckas en grupp civila manniskor fly. De upptacker att de ar bland de sista overlevande efter en utomjordisk invasion som har slukat inte bara deras land, utan hela planeten. Nar manskligheten faller under en varldsomfattande ockupation så omgrupperar de sin arme for att slå tillbaka mot de fullstandigt overlagsna fiendestyrkorna. I striderna vid fronten i slaget om planeten jorden ar de och de få kvarvarande militara forbanden mansklighetens allra sista hopp.

programme.title: Raising Wildlife
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Grey Duiker, Silverback Gorilla
programme.desc: In the Centre for Rehabilitation of Wildlife situated in KwaZulu Natal, South Africa, junior nurse Kylie is preparing grey duiker Major for his release into the wild. Major had suffered several injuries when he arrived at the centre, but with Kylie’s help he recovered, and he will soon be back in his natural environment. We also travel to the Eastern Cape in South Africa to the main port city called, Port Elizabeth. Here Ruth, a dedicated animal caretaker, is constantly monitoring her loggerhead turtle hatchling Rocky, who has trouble with weight fluctuations. But once his nutrition is balanced enough that he can keep his weight for several weeks, he can be released into the Indian...

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Baltic - Enchanted Forests and Moors
programme.desc: The wide, often untouched wilderness of the Baltic hinterland is home to many animals. More than 35 brown bears live in the primeval forests of Alutaguse. In the spring, the Soomaa National Park transforms into a huge lake. Europes widest waterfall is located in Latvia. In the beginning of May, vimba bream follow the course of the River Venta. The hardly 5-centimetre-long fish have to overcome a 4-metre-long rock barrier in order to reach their spawning grounds.

programme.title: The Moor
programme.desc: Moors and peatlands are oases in the cultivated landscape of Central Europe.

programme.title: Bosnia Herzegovina
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Bosnia and Herzegovina: The Abundant North
programme.desc: Wild and unknown lies the still undiscovered natural paradise of Bosnia and Herzegovina in the heart of Europe. Rough mountains, dense forests and wild waterfalls characterize the picture of the untouched landscapes. Lynx, wolves and bears roam mountains and valleys. One of the last primeval forests in Europe is a retreat for many endangered animal species. Bosnia and Herzegovina is actually an undiscovered natural paradise in the middle of Europe.

programme.title: Bosnia Herzegovina
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Bosnia and Herzegovina: The Karstic South
programme.desc: The barren, karstic south of the country, Herzegovina, also impresses with its natural landscapes. One of them is the Livno field. Not only is it the largest wetland in the country, it is also the largest regularly flooded karst field in the world. About 700 wild horses live in this unique landscape. Their ancestors were working horses that were abandoned here more than 50 years ago. Another special feature of the karst landscape are the rivers with their tufa barriers. The countless waterfalls that pour over it are a unique natural phenomenon.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The Parque Nacional Peneda-Geres is the only national park in Portugal. An area of almost 700 square kilometers, located in the extreme north of Portugal. Barren and rocky ridges in the plateaus, contrast with large forests and lush ground vegetation in deep valleys, crossed by lakes and rivers. The park is known for its oak forests, which are predominantly pedunculate and Pyrenean oaks. Among the typical animals of the park are the small Garrano ponies, a very old breed of horse and the only one in Europe that still lives in the wild.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The highest mountain range in Portugal is the Serra da Estrela. The episode embarks on a voyage of discovery to adventurous rock formations and villages steeped in tradition. The nature park is the largest protected area on the Iberian peninsula. In the mountain range we accompany the young scientist Ana Matos, who wants to breathe new life into old traditions, and cheese maker Maria Natália Lopes. She watches over more than 350 sheeps.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 South West Portugal: Alentejano and Costa Vicentina
programme.desc: In the southwest of Portugal lies the little known Parque Natural do Sudoeste Alentejano e Costa Vicentina. It encompasses a narrow coastal strip that runs along the coast to the south of Portugal. Sparsely populated, this coastal region, which was placed under protection in 1988, is considered one of the last intact ecosystems in Europe. The steep cliffs, the almost constant wind and high waves have ensured that mass tourism has not gained a foothold here. There are still near-natural forests and a diverse bird life.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: Madeira - Portugals autonomous island in the Atlantic Ocean, is closer to the African coast than to the mother country Portugal, from which it is separated by about 900 kilometers. The islands name comes from Portuguese sailors who claimed the uninhabited isle for themselves in 1419. Madeira means wood and that was available in abundance. Almost the entire surface was covered by dense forest. Since 1982, two-thirds of the landscape has been protected.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The "Parque Natural da Ria Formosa" is one of the largest lagoon conservation areas in Europe. Bordered by five natural islands. A mosaic of sandbanks, brackish and freshwater lagoons and salt marshes. In 2010, the "Ria Formosa" was chosen as one of the seven natural wonders of Portugal. It is a unique ecosystem: in the winter months, more than 20,000 birds gather here. In addition, the nature park has one of the largest seahorse populations internationally. More than half of all fish species in the Atlantic are said to spawn in the lagoon.

programme.title: Wilderness in Europe: The Bohemian Forest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Psychogramm of a Spiritual Landscape
programme.desc: The Bohemian Forest is the source of the Vltava River, home to primeval forests, untouched high moors and bubbling torrents. This archaic stretch of land, which includes the Bavarian Forest, was long considered impenetrable and mysterious. Since the fall of the Iron Curtain, Bavarian border residents have rediscovered new references to this unusual forest landscape for themselves. This is also the case with photo artist Bastian Kalous, who has been documenting his homeland for years with nostalgic-looking Polaroid photographs and is dealing with its eventful history for an illustrated book. Or Elisa Belotti and Marco Heurich, who have dedicated their lives to the lynxes. In order for...

programme.title: Wilderness in Europe: The Bohemian Forest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Boundary Experiences in Muhlviertel
programme.desc: Pavel Hubeny, whose life would be unthinkable without the forest, is the head of the Šumava National Park. He is committed to ensuring that a primeval forest can grow for future generations, in which man does not interfere. This vision of a primeval forest is also shared by the forester Claus Bassler, who wants to counteract the extinction of species by having trees felled to create artificial deadwood and thus a new habitat for rare beetles and fungi. On the Vltava River lies the small town of Krumlov, the "Pearl of the Bohemian Forest" with its Baroque theater and fully preserved stage technology from the 17th century. Here the director Zuzana Vrbová enchants people from all over the...

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.desc: The moon disappears behind the horizon and the stage is set for a new day in the Alps of Berchtesgaden.

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Bavaria - In The Shadow of the Watzmann.
programme.desc: Mighty and mysterious, King Watzmann sits above Germanys only alpine national park.

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Baltic - Life on the Amber Coast
programme.desc: The first episode of this two-part nature documentary presents the natural beauty of the shifting sand dunes of the Curonian Spit, the romantic beaches of the Latvian Baltic Sea and the island worlds of Estonia. Time and again, this deserted and almost untouched nature fascinates. In the winter, ringed seals give birth to their young on the pack ice. In the spring, Konik wild horse stallions fight fierce battles amongst themselves, while colourful European rollers fly through the dune forests. Lynxes wander through the coastal forests and in the orchid meadows turncoats and hoopoes find more than enough food. On the islands around Saaremaa in Estonia, grey seals hunt for fish. They share...

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Baltic - Enchanted Forests and Moors
programme.desc: The wide, often untouched wilderness of the Baltic hinterland is home to many animals. More than 35 brown bears live in the primeval forests of Alutaguse. In the spring, the Soomaa National Park transforms into a huge lake. Europes widest waterfall is located in Latvia. In the beginning of May, vimba bream follow the course of the River Venta. The hardly 5-centimetre-long fish have to overcome a 4-metre-long rock barrier in order to reach their spawning grounds.

programme.title: The Moor
programme.desc: Moors and peatlands are oases in the cultivated landscape of Central Europe.

programme.title: Dreams of the Settlers - An American Journey
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Through Utahs Canyons to Salt Lake City
programme.desc: It’s a dream route leading from the casino metropolis of Las Vegas, to Salt Lake City, the Mormon capital. It is a journey that follows the footsteps of the first settlers: the Mormons. They came to this desert belt of the United States during the second half of the 19th century to escape persecution and in search of the promised land. Some of them founded Las Vegas. Others moved through the canyons and over the mountains of the colossal Colorado Plateau, where they found water and pasture, to establish many small settlements. The landscapes through which they trekked, had and still have, a breathtaking and bizarre majestic beauty. Bryce Canyon, the hogbacks and the Escalante Staircase...

programme.title: Dreams of the Settlers - An American Journey
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Through Louisiana Along the Mississippi
programme.desc: The vast Delta of the Mississippi River is the gateway to the South of the United States. It always has been. This is where our journey begins: through Louisiana along the banks of the mighty river, to the big inland city of New Orleans, founded long ago by the French. Further inland, sugarcane plantations and the villas of their former owners stretch as far as the eye can see. To the north, we leave the river and, taking spectacular roads, we pass through the swamplands of the Mississippi, which were once impenetrable, serving as the ideal hideout for many a runaway. Bordering Texas, where the swamplands end, is the beginning of the vast cattle country. This is home to the last remaining...

programme.title: Dreams of the Settlers - An American Journey
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Along the Shores of the Great Lakes
programme.desc: The Great Lakes are among the most mythical landscapes of North America: endless water, endless forest. Many Native American peoples lived there; later European settlers followed on the heels of the white hunters and trappers. They hunted in the forests and transported their furs and other goods across the water to the south where a small river situated at the southern tip of Lake Michigan flows onward towards the southern states. The settlement that sprung up there was called Checagou by the Indians. Much later, the settlement was to be the first skyscraper city in the world: Chicago, the megacity on the Great Lake.

programme.title: Secrets of the Mediterranean
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Secrets of the Mediterranean, Ep.1
programme.desc: The contours of the Mediterranean have changed during the course of its history. Near Gibraltar, Africa was once connected to the European continent. When the land bridge at Gibraltar collapsed, the Mediterranean basin filled up again. The Suez Canal is today connected to the Red Sea. This route enables animals to reach the Mediterranean, where they cause problems.

programme.title: Secrets of the Mediterranean
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Secrets of the Mediterranean, Ep. 2
programme.desc: Rugged rocks, blue sea and idyllic, sandy beaches - this is the Mediterranean as we know it. But this impression is deceptive: the Mediterranean is under constant change. The continents are moving towards one another. Animals, that have to survive under such extreme conditions, must find a way to escape the dangers. Between deserts and volcanoes, the challenges for the animals are enormous.

programme.title: Germanys Wild Amazon
programme.desc: As one of Germany’s beauties, the river was the gem of Germanys landscape. But with industrialization it became the country’s hardest working river and like everything that has been overworked, it lost it magnificence and charm. Due to tender love and care, the river is now a reigning example of one of the most successful and outstanding renaturation projects in the country.The film shows never before seen shots of the river now pulsing with life. We will show you the winding river bed, spawning salmon, mating crabs and still-growing anchor ice. You will see dipper birds searching for food under water, kingfishers catching fish, a family life of badgers, foxes and a wide variety of birds....

programme.title: Germanys Wild Reservoirs
programme.desc: One of the smallest dams in the Bergisches Land is the Panzertalsperre, with an area of just four-and-a-half football pitches. On the other hand, the Dhunntalsperre is the largest with the area of 660 football pitches. They all transform a stretch of flowing water into still and stagnant water. As a result, completely diverse ecosystems have developed there: where the dipper once dived for insect larvae, cormorants and gray herons now fish and swans and coots cavort. In recent summers, even greater challenges have emerged: the effects of climate change - from extreme drought to destructive floods. On a smaller scale, a rather industrious dam master is operating flood protection: The...

programme.title: Germanys Mystic Forest
programme.desc: 2.000 rivers and streams dig deep into the underground and transport their water into reservoirs or "Germanys Wild Amazon", the Wupper. These forests and rivers, together with heathlands and moors, are home to a diverse fauna. Martens, badgers, wild boars, hares, roe deer, and red deer, even black grouse and hazel deer find shelter in these parts. Wolves also have a dominant presence, not to mention those who live underground, such as lizards, bats, and snakes. Accompany us on a journey where we explore every corner of this rugged land. Climb underground into the Bergisches Land, through the vast hidden cave systems that sprawl far beneath the forests. There is also much to be discovered...

programme.title: Northern Woods
programme.desc: It is a musical film a a tributeto the Nordic forest: it shows its development from a primeval wood to a cultivated forest. Once populated by wild animals such as wolves, bears, eagles, deer and musk oxen, complex re-enactment-scenes shot by dollies and helicopters vividly depict the colonization of the forest by the Celts and Germans. But as time progressed, the northern forest has on numerous occasions fallen victim to environmental degradation and overexploitation. Several provisions were made to protect this wild beauty. The Helsinki resolution of 1993, which stipulated that the woods be used in a way and in a magnitude which guarantees their biological variety and productiveness and...

programme.title: Poppys Promise - Secret Life in a Cornfield
programme.desc: The cornfield - just an area for producing food… or a land full of secrets? This doc portrays a little recognized habitat right next door. The spectacular visuals filmed with state of the art equipment introduce the surprisingly large diversity of field inhabitants. We follow a hamster family through a season full of adventures and are drawn into an unknown world – a world of which we thought we knew everything about. In the western industrial nations cornfields and woods take up the greatest proportion of rural land. But how much natural life dwells in a cornfield? Why are some cornfield inhabitants harmful and others useful and what do the colourful flowers at the edge of the field...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Secret World of Herbs - In Provence
programme.desc: Its native fragrant flowers and aromatic herbs have made the Provence a brand known worldwide. The wealth of flora found in this region, between the French Alps and the Mediterranean, is unequalled among the French provinces. Around Sault, near Mont Ventoux, the valleys and high plains are carpeted with bright violet: In the hot climate of the South of France, lavender blooms and exudes its fragrance. Monastic healers have been using its aromatic medicinal oil since the Middle Ages. And today an entire industry is based on the trade with this fragrant flower. Yet the livelihood of Provençal lavender farmers is imperiled. In France’s major lavender-growing region, the “Plateau de...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 The Secret World of Herbs - In India
programme.desc: In India, herbs play an everyday role hardly equalled anywhere in the world. From the tropical green south to the mountains of the northern Himalayas, herbs lend fragrance to joss sticks and soaps, and flavor to the cuisine. And, above all, herbs heal. Six thousand varieties of plants are used in India, and most are harvested in the wild – where they are becoming depleted. The ever rising need for herbal medicine for the subcontinent’s 1.3 billion inhabitants comes on top of the demand of its growing middle class for herbal-based cosmetics. As a result, certain herbs have become scarce, while others have already vanished entirely. Most of the herbs in India are harvested in the wild. The...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The Secret World of Herbs - In Latin America
programme.desc: Healing effects, fragrance, and intense flavor – the benefits of herbs were discovered by the indigenous peoples of South America long before Spanish conquistadores subdued the continent. Even today, in the remote regions of South America, life without herbs is unthinkable. For many inhabitants, they provide the sole medicine. For more than two thousand years, this wisdom of the healing powers of nature has been passed down from generation to generation. In Bolivia, the film accompanies ethnobiologist Rainer Bussmann on one of his expeditions documenting which herbs the locals use against which illnesses. The German scientist has spent the last 15 years in the region, focussed on...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 The Secret World of Herbs - In the Alps
programme.desc: Secluded for many centuries in inaccessible valleys, the inhabitants of the Alps had no alternative but to rely on the healing powers of nature. A knowledge of herbs was deeply rooted in these mountain-dwellers’ everyday lives – until the twentieth century, when this wisdom became eclipsed by modern academic medicine. Today, Alpine herbs are witnessing a revival, as public interest in regional natural treasures grows. The potential of Alpine herbs is far from exhausted. In the Berchtesgaden Alps, the film shows Hubsi Ilsanker at work as a root-digger, a back-breaking job that has scarcely changed in four hundred years. Authorized by a special historic permit to supply the oldest gentian...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The Secret world of Herbs - In the Balkans
programme.desc: In the pristine nature and mild climate of southeastern Europe grows a unique diversity of wild plants. Far removed from major industry and polluted soils, the Balkan countries have become the largest exporter of herbs in Europe. In Bulgaria alone, more than 300,000 people work with domestic plants. The business is becoming increasingly lucrative. The film takes us to the Croatian coast. On the Adriatic island of Cres, the audience meets Mladen Dragoslavić. In May, when the sage begins to blossom, this beekeeper has one month to produce his income for an entire year – always with the goal of creating the best sage honey in the Balkans. Given a choice, the bees would never choose sage, for...

programme.title: Italys Uncharted Islands
programme.desc: The Sulcis Archipelago is located off the south-western coast of Sardinia and is part of the province of of southern Sardinia. The islands of San Pietro, SantAntioco and Isola Piana form the archipelago, together with several uninhabited islets and rocks form the archipelago. It belongs to the less known areas in Italy and is little developed for tourism. Nevertheless stars like Tom Cruise and Roberto Cavalli come here to enjoy the peace, seclusion and good food. The islanders are only moderately interested in these visitors, and their down-to-earth attitude has never lost.

programme.title: Italys Uncharted Islands
programme.desc: Lake Iseo is located on the southern foothills of the Alps. It extends over the provinces of Brescia and Bergamo in the northern mainland of Italy. In the middle of Lake Iseo lies the largest island of the southern European inland waters. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. The teenager has been stabbed sixty times with a knife and -an extra sordid detail - a devil mask is found next to her body. Was Priscillia the victim of a prowler? A serial killer? A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. The man is lying in a pool of blood and, on his belly, the murderer has written "DIRTY RAPIST". Yet Jean-Raymond Blatti was never charged with sexual assault. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 19th 2004, the naked and tied up body of a woman is recovered in the Ourcq canal in Fresnes-sur-Marne. The victim is impossible to identify.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On April 3th 2003, Chantal Ternik, a 48 year old housewife, is discovered hanged in her house of Sanary-sur-Mer, in Var.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On March 28th 2013, the burnt body of Anne Barbot, 38 years old, is discovered in a forest of Maine-et-Loire.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On May 17th 2005, a body is discovered in a forest of Sucy-en-Brie; Christophe Belle, 40 years old, a renowned pastry cook.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The disturbing missing case in Paris of a four year old.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On October 13th 1996, the body of young Angelique Dumetz, 18 years old, is recovered down a ditch in Oise forest. An important clue is found on the crime scene.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On February 23th 2017, policemen are alerted of the disapearrance of Brigitte Troadec, her husband Pascal, and their children Sebastien and Charlotte.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Call Of The Wild

programme.desc: Childhood curiosity can build a lifelong passion for the natural world. What is special about women’s connection to the wild?

programme.title: Who Tells The Story?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Nature Through Her Eyes
programme.desc: Many of nature’s greatest champions are women. Can their storytelling help restore balance to a troubled world?

programme.title: Climbing The Mountain
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Nature Through Her Eyes
programme.desc: Our stories of the wilderness have traditionally been told by white men. But in recent decades pioneering women have overcome obstacles to make their voices heard.

programme.title: One World
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Nature Through Her Eyes
programme.desc: Partnerships between men and women, young and old, black and white, give us a fresh appreciation for the creatures we share this earth with.

programme.title: The Last Frontier
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: In Katmai National Park, Alaska a massive population of coastal brown bears gather to eat salmon as they migrate back to the rivers and streams where they were born.

programme.title: Fish Like a Bear
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: The crew heads inland to a section of the river to observe the many different families as they fish.

programme.title: A Working Ecosystem
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: During a lull in bear and salmon activity, Casey and the crew decide to head inland in search of the spawning fish.

programme.title: The Wolf and The Storm
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: After seeing a wolf in the distance and tracks on the shore, the crew head inland in search of more clues to the wolfs whereabouts.

programme.title: Neighbors, Old and New
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: Casey and the crew go out in search of the family of the lost cub from the previous night. They hope that if they find them, the cub will have found them as well.

programme.title: No Place Like Home
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 The Trackers Diary: Bears of Katmai
programme.desc: As the end of their expedition draws near, salmon and bear activity begins to decline, but that doesn’t mean that there aren’t some bears still lingering around the area.

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Enter the Void
programme.desc: Regissoren till 2000-talets mest okanda film ar tillbaka med ett verk som inte liknar något annat: en kanslomassigt omtumlande och visuellt overvaldigande mardromsresa genom liv, dod och återfodelse. Prisbelonade Enter the Void ar en mork, men inte desto mindre fargsprakande odysse sedd genom den doende huvudpersonens hallucinerande ogon. I Tokyos neonupplysta natt blir den unge knarklangaren Oscar skjuten. Vore det inte for hans syster hade historien slutat dar.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: The Dresser
programme.desc: En odesdiger natt på en liten engelsk teater under andra varldskriget, satter en trupp med kringresande skådespelare upp Shakespeares "King Lear".
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Bekas
programme.desc: Tidigt 90-tal, Saddam Husseins regim har satt stor press på den kurdiska delen av Irak. Två hemlosa kurdiska pojkar ser Superman på stadens forsta biograf och bestammer sig for att ta sig till Amerika. For att komma dit behover de pass, pengar och en hel del tur. Tyvarr har de inget av detta men de borjar andå resan som ska ta dem mot drommen om Amerika.

programme.title: Sommarminnen
programme.desc: Helène ar familjens matriark, och har agnat sitt liv åt att samla konst och antikviteter. Nar hennes liv till slut kommer till anda står hennes tre barn med ett stort arv i form av ett vackert gammalt lantgods och allt det huserar, men de ar allt annat an overens om hur dessa slaktklenoder ska forvaltas. Sommarminnen ar Guldpalmsvinnaren Olivier Assayas starka familjedrama med Juliette Binoche, Charles Berling och Jeremie Renier.

programme.title: From Time to Time
programme.desc: En spokhistoria som spanner over två varldar med mer an ett sekel från varandra. Nar 13-åriga Tolly upptacker att han på ett mystiskt satt kan resa mellan de två, borjar han ett aventyr som avslojar familjehemligheter som har begravts i generationer.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Camp X-Ray
programme.desc: Kristen Stewart spelar huvudrollen i Peter Sattlers hyllade debutfilm Camp X-Ray. Hon spelar Amy Cole, en ung kvinna som tar varvning i amerikanska militaren i tron att hon kommer att skickas till Irak eller Afghanistan. Istallet blir hon stationerad som vakt på ett okant militarfangelse, med tuffa villkor for såval basens fångar som de få kvinnliga militarer som arbetar dar.

programme.title: Synchronicity
programme.desc: "Fysikern Jim Beale har uppfunnit en maskin som kommer att revolutionera varlden som vi kanner den: en tidsresemaskin som kroker rumtid. Nar Klaus Meisner, en av varldens maktigaste foretagare, får veta det så beslutar han att han till varje pris måste ha maskinen. Nar Jim med maskinen oppnar ett maskhål så dyker det upp en dahlia från framtiden. For att behålla ratten till sin uppfinning måste Jim bevisa att maskinen fungerar genom att hitta blommans identiska motsvarighet i nuet. Jim upptacker snart att dahlian ags av Abby, en mystisk kvinna som forfor honom for att han ska avsloja sina hemligheter.

programme.title: Amores Perros
programme.desc: Karlek ar många saker — vissa bra, andra dåliga — men framfor allt suger den. En fruktansvard bilolycka binder samman tre berattelser, var och en med karaktarer som hanterar forlust, ånger och livets hårda verkligheter, allt i karlekens namn.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: The Dark Divide
programme.desc: En dramakomedi som baserar sig på verkliga handelser, med David Cross - som vi sett i serien Arrested Development, och Debra Messing - kand från serien Will and Grace, i huvudrollerna. Robert ar en fjarilsforskare vars fru insjuknar i cancer. Frun overtalar sin uppgivne man att åka på en fjarilsresa, vars ovantade moten och forvantade motgångar oppnar Roberts ogon på nytt.

programme.title: Shattered Glass
programme.desc: Hayden Christensen spelar huvudrollen i denna kritikerrosade berattelse om en utskamd journalist, regisserad och samskriven av Billy Ray, Oscar®-nominerad forfattare av KAPTEN PHILLIPS. Nar den beromda journalisten Stephen Glass (Christensen) plotsligt utredas av en Forbes.com-reporter (Steve Zahn) avslojar sokandet att Glass har diktat ihop många av sina sensationella berattelser, vilket leder till hans ultimata fall i detta gripande, faktabaserade drama.

programme.title: Birdman
programme.desc: I den omtalade och kritikerhyllade svarta komedin BIRDMAN eller The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance ser vi Michael Keaton i huvudrollen som en skådespelare, mest kand for att ha spelat den ikoniska superhjalten Birdman. Han ska nu regissera en teateruppforestallning på Broadway och vi får folja honom under de hektiska dagarna innan den stora premiarkvallen. Samtidigt som han slåss mot sina inre demoner och sitt stora ego så forsoker han lappa ihop både familj och karriar. For regi står Alejandro G. Iñárritu (BABEL, ÄLSKADE HUNDAR) och i ovriga roller ser vi bl.a. Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton, Emma Stone, Naomi Watts.

programme.title: Klanen - berattelsen om Grudornas slakt
programme.desc: "Klanen" ar historien om en brottslig slakt dar Mika Kaurismaki behandlar existensens villkor genom den traditionella episka formen, på gransen mellan ratt och fel i lagen. Alexander, den yngsta sonen, ar slaktens vita får. Han forvantas hålla sig på den raka vagen, till skillnad från sin far och andra man i slakten. Men familjen ar varst, och blod ar tjockare an vatten... Familjedramat "Klanen" ar en storslagen hyllning till den gamla finska filmen.

programme.title: Bekas
programme.desc: Tidigt 90-tal, Saddam Husseins regim har satt stor press på den kurdiska delen av Irak. Två hemlosa kurdiska pojkar ser Superman på stadens forsta biograf och bestammer sig for att ta sig till Amerika. For att komma dit behover de pass, pengar och en hel del tur. Tyvarr har de inget av detta men de borjar andå resan som ska ta dem mot drommen om Amerika.

programme.title: Dont Come Knocking
programme.desc: Hollywoodstjarnan Howard Spence (Sam Shepard) har sett battre dagar. Han vilar på sina lagrar och lever på sin gamla stjarnstatus. Efter ytterligare en natt med vilda utsvavningar flyr han från inspelningen av nasta vasternfilm och rider ut på prarien och de stora vidderna precis som en av hjaltarna som han så ofta har gestaltat. Han soker tillflykt hemma hos sin mamma (Eva Marie Saint) som han inte har traffat på många år. Men inte ens dar stannar han sarskilt lange, for han får veta att han någonstans kan ha en son som han inte visste fanns. For Howard kanns det som en strimma hopp och ett bevis for att inte har levt sitt liv forgaves.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: A Woman In Berlin
programme.desc: Våren 1945. Andra varldskriget narmar sig slutet då den roda armen marscherar in i Berlin. En kvinnlig journalist och fotograf som går under namnet Anonyma har tillbringat krigets sista månader i en kallare tillsammans med andra kvinnor som gommer sig i den sonderbombade staden. Efter att ha klarat sig undan krigetsharjningar står de ångestfyllda kvinnorna framfor ryska soldater som betraktar dem som krigsbyten. Desperat efter att finna någon som kan beskydda henne mot befrielsestyrkans systematiska misshandel och våldtakter narmar sig Anonyma en rysk officer och inleder ett forbjudet forhållande…

programme.title: The Vanishing
programme.desc: Tre man anlander till en obebodd o utanfor Skottlands kust for att vakta ons fyr. En dag upptacker de en medvetslos man som ligger i vattenbrynet, och bredvid honom en stor kista med guld... Det som sedan foljer ar en kamp om overlevnad orsakad av paranoia, isolering och girighet. Gerard Butler (300, Angel Has Fallen) briljerar i rollen som den hederliga familjefadern som pressas till det yttersta av mystiska omstandigheter. Filmen ar regisserad av danska Kristoffer Nyholm (Taboo, Brottet) och i rollistan syns också danska Søren Malling (Gisslantagningen, Kriget) i en framtradande biroll. Filmen ar baserad på verkliga handelser.

programme.desc: En hjartekrossad ung kvinna återvander hem over julen- och kanner pressen av att vara singel. Hennes karleksfulla och nyfikna syster planerar en natdejt- med en stilig idrottsman. Men det tar en ovantad vandning nar han inte ar hennes "prins i skinande rustning". Hennes barndomsvan visar henne att akta karlek kan finnas narmare hemmet.

programme.title: Jul under Wraps

programme.title: Christmas Land

programme.title: Julens Underland
programme.desc: Jultiden i NYC ar allt annat an underbar for den kampande artisten Heidi Neill.

programme.title: En Jadrans Jul
programme.desc: En hund med telepatiska formågor undkommer en regeringskontroll- och springer rakt i armarna på två unga broder. Men Washington-hojdarna ger inte upp sitt hemliga vapen så latt.

programme.title: En Bennett-sång Holiday
programme.desc: Familjen Bennett-Song återvander till jul med stora nyheter. Mrs Song vantar ett barn som ska utoka listan på 14 adopterade barn! Familjen måste samarbeta for att ta sig an en maktig byggherre- som vill stanga farbrors kulturhus for handikappade och utsatta barn. Lite karlek, lagarbete och julmagi kommer att radda dagen.

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Efter en prestigefull gala bestammer sig prinsessan Carly for att ta ett sabbatsår och hoppa på ett for henne dromjobb vid en skidanlaggning. Ingen av hennes nya arbetskamrater kanner till hennes ratta identitet, men nar medlemmar från den kungliga slakten borjar dyka upp vid anlaggningen blir det plotsligt valdigt komplicerat att hålla på hemligheten utan att bli upptackt. Allt medan de preppar for ett 50års jubileum av anlaggningen, och Carly som borjar bli stortkar i agarens bror Jesse. Carly står nu infor stora vagval i livet och kanner sig bara alltmer forvirrad ju langre tiden går…

programme.title: Elfette Raddar Julen
programme.desc: Nar tomten kidnappas av New York-maffian strax fore jul, kommer Elfette, en speciell nisse, till undsattning. Hon och hennes van Sparkle ska stoppa skurkarna, hitta tomten och radda julen.

programme.title: En perfekt jullista
programme.desc: Som en sista onskan ger en sjuk mormor sin dotter Michelle och barnbarnet Sara en lista over festliga prestationer att gora tillsammans fore jul, i hopp om att det ska reparera deras forhållande.

programme.title: Nyckeln till Julen
programme.desc: Nar en missnojd nisse ser sin chans att ta over Nordpolen- anvander hon en magisk maskin for att vrida tillbaka tiden på tomten- och han borjar bli yngre...och snabbt! Med tomtemor fångad och i polkagrisfangelse ar det upp till en lojal nisse, en liten flicka med en magisk nyckel och den nu tonårstomte att vrida fram tidens hander och radda julens framtid.

programme.title: High Holiday
programme.desc: Den frisinnade Liz ar inte så sugen på att ta med sin pojkvan hem till sin konservativa familj på julmiddag. Liz pojkvan foreslår att hon ska krydda salladsdressingen med marijuana for att latta upp stamningen. Kaos uppstår nar alla blir omedvetet hoga och avslojar familjens innersta hemligheter.

programme.desc: Madea sprider sin alldeles egen unika julstamning nar hon blir overtalad att spendera julen ute på landet med en van och hennes familj.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Stilla natt, heliga natt - Joseph Mohrs heroiska resa 1818, nar han skapade varldens mest kanda julsång. Den sanna historien om låten berattas som en fiktiv historia.

programme.title: Julharmoni
programme.desc: En begåvad sångerska blir forkrossad- nar hennes musikerpojkvan gor slut strax fore julhelgen. Hon återvander till sin hemstad dar hon traffar gamla vanner- och traffar en stilig ungkarl som också har upplevt hjartesorg. Tillsammans återupptacker de musik, romantik, familjeband- och julens magi.

programme.title: A Merry Holiday
programme.desc: Christy, en mycket framgångsrik forsaljare stressar over att landa en stor affar. Till sin hjalp tar hon medarbetaren Jonathan som ar upptagen med att pynta sin ungkarlslya till ett magiskt vinterland for att impa på flickvannens pappa. De kommer båda i klinch med varann, men inser att de måste samarbeta och hjalpa varandra. Ju mer tid de spenderar, desto avslappnat blir relationen dem emellan och kanske ar det inte bara jobbet som for dem samman langre?

programme.title: 12 Julhundar: Valpraddning
programme.desc: Barnen i Doverville kampar mot tiden och omojliga odds- for att radda ett hundbarnhem från en skrupelfri magnat.

programme.title: A Christmas Coincedence
programme.desc: Julen narmar sig med stormsteg och Paula har lite motvilligt accepterat hennes pojkvans frieri. Mormor Jane kanner att något inte står ratt till och bjuder hem henne på vischan for lite pepptalk. Paula besoker en vingård i narheten och springer in i agaren Gery. En serie tillfalligheter for dem narmare varann. Ett ovader sveper over bygden som tvingar Paula att stanna over natten, och snart kommer hon inse att just de ar menade for varann…

programme.title: Julkupong
programme.desc: En fore detta skridskomastare borjar undervisa vid sin vans damm- och delar ut "kuponger" for att locka nya elever. Nar hennes fore detta ungdomskarlek (och nu kand hockeyspelare) tar med sin brorsdotter på lektioner, tands gamla flammor på nytt, och julen fylls med en andra chans for karlek.

programme.title: Jul med en Krona
programme.desc: Nar en framgångsrik kvinna återvander till sin hemstad- traffar hon en stilig framling som hjalper till att organisera evenemanget. Det slår gnistor mellan dem, men hon anar inte att han ar en forkladd prins- som langtar efter julens sanna anda. Det kravs ett julmirakel av kungliga proportioner- for att deras hjartan ska bli ett.

programme.title: A Christmas Horror Story

programme.title: P2
programme.desc: En kvinna som jobbar sent på julafton blir tillfångatagen av en psykotisk sakerhetsvakt som ar besatt av henne. Med inga andra manniskor i parkeringshuset måste hon anvanda all sin list och styrka for att overleva och ta sig darifrån.

programme.title: Fatman
programme.desc: I dagens minst sagt skruvade varld finns jultomten på riktigt och han ar pank eftersom det knappt finns några snalla barn nufortiden och for att regeringen vagrar hjalpa honom med hans personalkostnader nar efterfrågan sjunker och intakterna sinar. Han ar en hårdsupande hårding som ar bevapnad, for nar man flyger jorden runt så kan folk ibland få for sig att skjuta tillbaka.

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsakringsman som kampar med forlust och karlek upptacker nya mojligheter under en vecka full av ovantade handelser och komiska vandpunkter.

programme.title: Degueyo English
programme.desc: When Ramons bandits storm Danger City for rumored treasure, they slaughter or capture the men, leaving only women and children to face a ruthless "Deguello" if the money isn’t found. Four determined men, already hunting Ramon, join forces to help the town defend itself.

programme.title: The Avenging Angel
programme.desc: Miles Utley, a skilled Mormon commando and bodyguard, is forced to go rogue while investigating a deadly scandal of assassination and land speculation. As danger mounts, he must confront his beliefs and decide where his true loyalties lie in a world of betrayal and faith.

programme.title: Rimfire
programme.desc: Captain Tom Harvey, an undercover army agent, investigates stolen army gold shipments. Posing as a deputy sheriff, he is drawn into solving the mystery of a ghost haunting the town. The ghost is believed to be the spirit of a gambler wrongly hanged for the thefts. Harveys investigation leads him to uncover a dark truth behind the ghostly terror.

programme.title: Pray to God and Dig Your Grave
programme.desc: Fernando returns from exile in Texas seeking revenge for his siblings deaths. But instead of personal vengeance, he’s driven to spark a revolution against the oppressive landowners, transforming his mission into a fight for justice and freedom.

programme.title: Lightning Jack
programme.desc: Lightning Jack Kane is an Australian outlaw in the wild west. During a bungled bank robbery he picks up mute Ben Doyle as a hostage. The two become good friends, with Jack teaching Ben how to rob banks, while they plan Jacks last heist.

programme.title: Joshua The Black Rider
programme.desc: A black soldier returns from fighting for the Union in the Civil War only to find out that his mother has been murdered by a gang of white thugs.

programme.title: Ringo, the Mark of Vengeance
programme.desc: Two adventurers rescue a man bearing a tattooed treasure map on his back. But the quest is far from over—the second crucial map is tattooed on a sheriff’s back. Together, they embark on a thrilling hunt, facing danger and mystery in pursuit of hidden riches.

programme.title: The Son of Zorro
programme.desc: In imperial Mexico, nobleman Don Ricardo secretly fights as the Son of Zorro against corrupt Governor Leblanche. When rebels ambush a weapons transport, killing Don Herrera, Ricardo rescues his daughter Conchita and hides her, fueling a revolution for justice and freedom.

programme.title: Ultimate Gunfighter
programme.desc: Two family clans have always been enemies; they spend their time hating and killing each other. The daughter of the Campos family and the son of the Mounter family fall in love, thus causing further hatred and deaths.

programme.title: The Shooting
programme.desc: A mysterious woman persuades two cowboys to help her in a revenge scheme.

programme.title: Seven Guns for the MacGregors
programme.desc: Ranch owner MacGregor has seven sons and oldest Gregor leads his brothers to Las Mesas, a small town where they want to sell horses. They get into trouble with local people who are related with evil Santillana. After getting imprisoned and losing their horses they decide to go after Santillanas gang.

programme.title: Guns Of The Revolution
programme.desc: In Mexico, a mad general is leading his own war against the Church.

programme.title: Arizona Colt Returns
programme.desc: Famed gunman Arizona Colt is sent by Moreno to rescue his daughter from the grips of Arizonas old enemy, Keane. But certain complications make the mission far more dangerous than expected.

programme.title: Django Kill... If You Live, Shoot!
programme.desc: Various factions, feud over stolen gold in a surreal town.

programme.title: Hellgate
programme.desc: Accused of spying for the Confederacy, a man is sent to the brutal Hellgate Prison. After a failed escape lands him in solitary confinement, his path to redemption begins. When a deadly plague strikes the prison, he faces the ultimate test of character, transforming his dire circumstances into a chance for renewal.

programme.title: The Gay Amigo
programme.desc: Mistaken for bandits, Cisco and Pancho are captured by the Captain, who releases them to track the real gang. Cisco discovers the true leaders are the editor and blacksmith. Using cunning, he sows distrust between them, gains the blacksmith’s trust, and joins the gang, setting up a trap to bring the criminals to justice.

programme.title: Boot Hill Bandits
programme.desc: Shady town businessman Bolton seems to be the leader of the gang but even he takes his order from a higher authority who may have tried to take Marshal Corrigans life.

programme.title: The Return of Jack Slade
programme.desc: Jack Slade, son of a legendary lawman, infiltrates a ruthless gang of outlaws to bring them down from within. After his friend is killed, Slade sets a deadly trap with the help of a Pinkerton agent. Deception, betrayal, and revenge ride hard in this classic Western showdown.

programme.title: Yellow Hair and the Fortress of Gold
programme.desc: Fiery blonde half-breed Yellow Hair and her easygoing sidekick the Pecos Kid are after a fortune in Mayan gold.

programme.title: Bonanza Compilation Episodes 28, 29, 30
programme.desc: The Wild West adventures of Ben Cartwright and his sons as they run and defend their Nevada ranch while helping the surrounding community.

programme.title: Watch Out Gringo! Sabata Will Return

programme.title: Mackenzies Raiders EP29-32

Grant and Secretary of War William W. Belknap to stop bandits from crossing the Rio Grande into the United States, or from returning to Mexico.

programme.title: And the Crows Will Dig Your Grave
programme.desc: After the Civil War, Wells Fargo hires pistoleros to protect against increasing banditry. Jeff Sullivan, driven by revenge for the brutal murder of his wife by Glenn Kovacks and his gang, joins the effort. Sullivan partners with Pancho Corrales and pursues Kovacks, using Kovacks stepbrother, Dan, as leverage. Their final confrontation leads to a deadly showdown.

programme.title: Yellowneck
programme.desc: A disgraced Confederate colonel deserts and escapes into the Everglades, joining four other Southern deserters. Surrounded by hostile Seminoles, the group must navigate the treacherous swamp while confronting both nature and their inner demons in a tense fight for survival.

programme.title: Deadly Trackers
programme.desc: Jeff sets out to murder each one of the five outlaws who robbed, raped and killed his poor sister.

programme.title: Buddy Goes West
programme.desc: Two outlaws, "The Doctor" and the Indian Girolamo, help a village fight a gang and a corrupt sheriff who has discovered gold beneath the town.

programme.title: My Name is Pecos
programme.desc: Everyone wants to know who the Mexican is. He always answer slowly, "my name is Pecos". Pecos Martinez to be exact, and hes returned to his hometown of Houston to settle up with Clain, the leader of a gang of cut-throats. Clain is busy looking for the money from a recent robbery thats been stolen from him. Soon the stolen cash in Pecos vengeance entwine and all hell breaks loose. Behind the scenes a Bible touting Undertaker (Umberto Raho), a cowardly saloon owner, and a helpful saloon girl become part of the story. This film made Woods as internationally known as Pecos in the third world countries as Franco Nero was known for Django. A Mexican hero against a gang and a town full of...

programme.title: Incredible Rocky Mountain Race
programme.desc: An old man observes a boy bullying his playmates and treats him to a morality lesson. The man tells the story of the epic cross-country race between a young Mark Twain and his rival, Mike Fink.

programme.title: White Fang and the Gold Diggers
programme.desc: Sandy Shaw inherits the "Eagles Nest" gold mine in Canadas wild north. With his son Rick and dog Whiskey, he faces Taft, a ruthless rival eager to claim the mine. When Sandy’s proxy bride arrives, the clash of greed, revenge, and betrayal turns deadly in this fight for survival.

programme.title: Running Target
programme.desc: In the Colorado Rockies, Sheriff Scott, heads a posse that is after four escaped convicts, and thought it is his sworn duty to return the men dead or alive, he is, as always, reluctant to kill his fellow man.

programme.title: Buckskin Frontier
programme.desc: A railroad man and the owner of a freight line battle for control of a crucial mountain pass.

programme.title: Gentleman Killer
programme.desc: A quiet border town erupts into chaos as tensions rise between the US and Mexico. The cause? A ruthless Mexican bandit determined to kill as many US soldiers as possible. As political turmoil intensifies, the town becomes the center of a deadly conflict, where vengeance, power, and survival collide.

Forsvunna pass, tågstrejker och ovantade romantiska forvecklingar satter vanskapen på spel. Frågan ar: Hinner de i tid for att hedra sin vans minne?

programme.title: Uptown Girls

Ray (Fanning) ar en kravande nioårig flicka vars senaste barnflicka precis slutat. Nar Rays alltfor upptagna mamma (Heather Locklear) anstaller Molly som Rays nya barnflicka ar det den perfekta chansen for båda flickorna att andra sina vanor och upptacka att ibland kan din basta van komma i den mest ovantade formen!

programme.title: Movie 43

programme.title: Barbershop
programme.desc: Ice Cube, Anthony Anderson, Sean Patrick Thomas, Eve och Cedric the Entertainer spelar huvudrollerna i denna hysteriskt roliga komedi om en barbershop i Chicago dar knivskarp humor aldrig går ur tiden! Calvin (Ice Cube) ar en blivande entreprenor med stora planer... och att driva sin familjs barbershop ar inte en av dem. Men nar han impulsivt saljer butiken till en skum lånehaj inser han snart hur viktig kvartersalongen ar for honom... och hur långt han ar beredd att gå for att få tillbaka den!

programme.title: Management

Och en misslyckad motelldirektor med smak for billig champagne och runda bakdelar? Ingen vinnarkombination, men mycket kan handa på ett ensligt motell... Hur som helst ar motellchefen Mike snart på vag tvars over USA for att forklara affarskvinnan Sue sin karlek - och forhindra att hon gifter sig med sin mycket beskyddande och inte sarskilt alskvarda fastman!

programme.title: Disaster Movie

Asteroider, tornados, jordbavningar och hela alltet, drabbar staden och deras vag då de forsoker losa en rad gåtor for att få ett slut på den okontrollerade forstorelsen.

programme.title: The Details

Men nar en familj av tvattbjornar invaderar deras perfekta tradgård blir Jeff besatt av att utrota djuren med alla mojliga medel. Kampen mot skadesdjuren startar en flirt med den vackra grannen Lila (Laura Linney), och innan han vet ordet av har han inlett en absurd spiral av otrohet, utpressning och organdonation.

programme.title: Dina, mina och våra (Yours, Mine and Ours)

En ankeman som ar kustbevakningsamiral och en anka som ar handvaskedesigner blir kara och gifter sig, till stor fortret for hennes 10 och hans 8 barn. Nar barnen planerar att skilja sina foraldrar inser de att det viktigaste ar familjen.

programme.title: Shriek If You Know What I Did Last Friday the 13th

programme.title: A Haunted House 2

Efter att ha flyttat in i deras dromhem plågas Malcolm återigen av bisarra paranormala handelser, och den har gången ar det inte bara huset som ar hemsokt! Jamie Pressly, Cedric the Entertainer och Essence Atkins medverkar också.

programme.title: The Beach Bum

I rollistan ser vi stjarnor som Snoop Dogg, Isla Fisher, Zac Efron, Jimmy Buffet, Martin Lawrence och Jonah Hill. The Beach Bum ar en ny, originell och revolutionerande komedi av manusforfattaren och regissoren Harmony Korine.

programme.title: The Rules of Attraction - Lustans lagar

programme.title: Paper Man

I ett forsok att återvinna sin forna storhet som forfattare, skickas han ivag till Cape Cod av sin fru Claire (LISA KUDROW) for att skriva sin andra roman. Men då Captain Excellent foljer med som kumpan och hejarklack blir livet dar inte riktigt som planerat... Den 17-åriga flickan Abby (EMMA STONE), vars tragiska forflutna har lett henne till att fly in i sina fantasier, ansluter sig till sallskapet, och en mycket speciell vanskap uppstår.

programme.title: Peace, Love and Misunderstanding

Det var tankt att bli en avkopplande helgutflykt men som snabbt forvandlas till en sommar fylld med aventyr, romantik, musik, familjehemligheter och om att hitta sig sjalv.

programme.title: Trinity klipper till igen

Ja faktiskt, for de ar sjalva ute efter att håva in formogenheten. Och for att vinna guld kommer de offra mycket bly.Men till skillnad från andra vilda fighter och skottdueller finns har många vinnare. Vapentillverkare, bandageforsaljare och dodgravare till exempel. Och framforallt lakarna som måste ta hand om alla som skrattat kakarna ur led! Terence Hill and Bud Spencer ar ett av filmhistoriens popularaste hjaltepar, som dunkat skurkar ihop I nitton filmer!

Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: The Deadly Companions
programme.desc: An unholy alliance! Marking the feature film debut of one of Hollywoods most influential and widely referenced auteur directors, Sam Peckinpah, The Deadly Companions centers on a redemptive journey to escort a funeral procession through dangerous Indian Territory. Featuring fine work from a top-notch cast that includes the inimitable Maureen OHara at the height of her illustrious career, Peckinpahs first foray into film provides a promising glance into the energetic and violent nature of his iconic later works.

With a cast that includes Frances Rich and Bud Osborne, this action tale from director Harry L. Fraser (The Last of the Clintons) is another forgotten classic from Monogram Pictures.

programme.title: The Hanged Man
programme.desc: After a condemned gunfighter (Steve Forrest) survives his own hanging, he helps a young widow stop a pitiless land baron from taking her ranch. This television feature boasts a strong cast of recognizable characters, including Will Geer, Sharon Acker, Dean Jagger, BarBara Luna, and Cameron Mitchell. Director Michael Caffey would go on to work on such hit shows as Barnaby Jones and MacGyver. Also, look for John Mitchum, younger brother of Robert, in a small role. This movie originally aired on ABC-TV and was considered the pilot for a possible series. Writer/producer Andrew Fenady was behind several opular TV shows such as Branded and The Rebel, as well as the 1970 John Wayne feature, Chisum.

programme.title: Rawhide
programme.desc: Baseball superstar Gehrig is one of several ranchers being coerced by a bunch of bandits. His sister and her lawyer/lover organize the ranchers. Directed by Ray Taylor; starring Smith Ballew, Gehrig, Evelyn Knapp. Talk about stunt casting! Gehrig was a New York Yankees star who was nearing the end of his career, but one of the biggest sports stars in the country. In the movie he plays a variation of himself, as Lou Gehrig, a retired baseball player who takes up ranching. Lou expects to relax on his ranch but quickly joins other ranchers in a fight to protect their properties.

programme.title: The Star Packer
programme.desc: He Dared Death In The Outlaws Lair! John Travers (John Wayne) takes on a mysterious gang leader known as The Shadow in this vintage western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Director/writer Robert N. Bradbury (Blue Steel, Riders of Destiny) gets the best of a remarkable cast that includes George Gabby Hayes. Of interest to film buffs is that the feature was shot in various California locations by Oscar winning cinematographer Archie Stout (The Quiet Man).

programme.title: The Sundowners
programme.desc: Brother battles brother in this gritty tale of feuding ranchers in the old west. This story of the Texas panhandle stars such familiar faces as Robert Preston, Chill Wills, and Jack Elam, and was a rare film for its time in that it was filmed almost entirely in Texas with no studio interiors. If for no other reason, watch this one for Prestons performance. If you only know him from The Music Man or Victor Victoria, youre sure to be surprised here! (also, look for John Drew Barrymore as Jef Cloud. He was part of the famous Barrymore family, and father of Drew Barrymore.) Jim Strake: Frank Cordell. The Whip: Dave Kashner. Directed by George Templeton

The first sound film for Hollywood heavyweight Clark Gable, The Painted Desert finds Boyd and Gable at odds over the affections of a cowboys beautiful daughter (Helen Twelvetrees).
